   Webb D 1984 pp 206 [RAIN, TEMP, TEXT, PH, DRA, DEP, LIG, KTMP, USE]
   Edwards S 1984 pp 223
   National RC 1980 pp 143
   INSPIRE species 123 [RAIN, TEMP, TEXT, PH, DRA, DEP, LIG, USE]

